{"tid":970179,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【血的教訓】網友打機買人中之龍0 被指勾結黑幫險被凍結帳號","createTime":"2019-01-05T15:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T04:35:23.000Z","uid":229553,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3397573f746596d2452ef83fc6e32efe3cc86b13","tid":970179,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"game名好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為什麼買個遊戲就會導致帳號慘遭凍結呢？<span style=\"color: red;\">原來，是因為「Prince of Yharnam」在買遊戲時，按照以往的習慣把遊戲名稱寫在了交易描述裡，而《人中之龍0 誓言的場所》的英文名「Yakuza」意為「極道」，亦意指有組織犯罪活動或從事暴力的人士或團體。於是，這位朋友只是想買個叫「Yakuza 0」的遊戲，卻被paypal誤以為是和犯罪組織進行交易</span>，差點就被凍結了帳號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fighterstudiohk.com/news/%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%E8%B2%B7%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%8B%E9%BE%8D0-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%AB%E9%9A%AA%E8%A2%AB%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fighterstudiohk.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25A9%259F%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%25BE%258D0-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258B%25BE%25E7%25B5%2590%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E9%259A%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E8%2599%259F%2F&d=bXOg%2FiaxOvVhA0i%2Fv%2FEqqh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=c5eca629\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fighterstudiohk.com/news/%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%E8%B2%B7%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%8B%E9%BE%8D0-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%AB%E9%9A%AA%E8%A2%AB%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F/</a>"},{"pid":"9077ff8ebe1017729f9ff4d8fb1dc34bcb1b1cd2","tid":970179,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"連登無人玩人中?<img src=\"/asset